        "text": "=Rewrite this LinkedIn post to sound more natural and human. Keep the key points but make it conversational and authentic:\n\n{{ $json.linkedinPost }}\n\nOutput ONLY the rewritten post text itself, starting directly with the post content. Do not include a title, headers, explanations, rationale, character counts, tables, or any commentary about the changes you made. Do not wrap it in quotes.",
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "You are an expert at making AI-generated content sound natural and human. Maintain professionalism while adding warmth and authenticity. You must respond with ONLY the rewritten post text — never include titles, section headers, explanations, rationale, character counts, tables, or any meta-commentary about what you changed or why."
        }
